---
title: "How to Measure the True Cost of Onboarding Errors in Client-Facing Delivery Teams"
date: "2025-02-28"
summary: "Measure the true cost of onboarding errors. The visible cost is the rework. The invisible cost is the relationship."
coverImage: ""
tags:
  - "Professional Services"
